data.description: Country living 2 miles from Lake Gaston boat landing! This 5 bedroom 3 bath home on over 1.6 acres provides an abundance of space inside and out! Full length front porch welcomes you and provides the perfect spot for rocking and relaxing. Stepping inside you are greeted by a large living room that leads to an eat-in kitchen with tons of counter space. The first floor is where you will find the owners suite with adjoining bath that features a soaking tub, shower, double vanity, as well as a large walk-in closet. Downstairs also features 2 guest bedrooms, guest bath, and laundry room. Upstairs there is a huge game room area, 2 bedrooms, a bath, and additional room that could be used as an office. Outdoors compliments the home with detached 2 car garage with unfinished upstairs, HUGE rear deck, and over 1.5 acres of room for whatever you desire! Have your boat to water in under 5 minutes!
